{"tid":732112,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係點學游水","createTime":"2018-07-06T17:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T15:50:55.000Z","uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"384bd2afb3c1fefdf603c88ac741e5c8c1ad7ec7","tid":732112,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"點去克服水湧過上頭 果種恐懼? 只要一諗到呢樣就好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf6b332940ff46a3e97ce0d748c93e22ee54fb0","tid":732112,"uid":181217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:42:29.000Z","msg":"比fd推落深水池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f72340b60caad06e5473f6bbab4d02f4d557a9","tid":732112,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"比fd推落大池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e796d05047226fa548fda2eb45503391381a771","tid":732112,"uid":181822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"細個呀媽帶去學<br />\n試下係池邊練下踢腳練下手一步一步慢慢學"},{"pid":"1e503f23131c1b4c2c1becf005d263663a6ca9b1","tid":732112,"uid":139139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:44:01.000Z","msg":"自然識<br />\n可能三四歲已經去游水<br />\n所以天生唔驚水同埋郁下就會向前"},{"pid":"66161d382ee5d0ca8b0b04b951d17908194cb3bf","tid":732112,"uid":15823,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"係大池浸親幾次就識，跳落池之前同救生員講一講你唔識游水就安全好多"},{"pid":"2a77b58f1bb51d150d5cac8bc91874d1b4070b0c","tid":732112,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:44:40.000Z","msg":"咁你平時點洗面"},{"pid":"2207d0501d951e4158bc1d5fcc9c49f525b22f8f","tid":732112,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"第一次學就浸親<br />\n到依家都唔識游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0577b57fcd8a935c37a49cdb8e09af3c0a0b64a","tid":732112,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T00:36:36.000Z","msg":"弱智仔先驚水"},{"pid":"2627977042690028505fb54bfbfdeccf76439def","tid":732112,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0577b57fcd8a935c37a49cdb8e09af3c0a0b64a","tid":732112,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T00:36:36.000Z","msg":"弱智仔先驚水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"cf1eea709cee28a5b5d3b80ee95654470adafed1","tid":732112,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a77b58f1bb51d150d5cac8bc91874d1b4070b0c","tid":732112,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:44:40.000Z","msg":"咁你平時點洗面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"無洗過面"},{"pid":"765c4fd771a68537dc46000a56e03965282306f4","tid":732112,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c4a22e4f9b0faa8a1cd7a158fe208440a7b48d5","tid":732112,"uid":33749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"喺淺水池學識未水(潛落水面下)用鼻呼氣<br />\n個頭岳高上水面用口吸氣<br />\n咁就唔會濁親<br />\n用鼻吸氣就九成九會濁親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慣咗之後吸大啖氣面朝下咁潛<br />\n你會發覺個人會浮浮地<br />\n好難沉落去水底<br />\n<br />\n學識咗換氣嘅話就係成咗一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4a0e4e0aed9feec97bd9629aad6a5d89b91c36","tid":732112,"uid":138040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"我係上youtube 睇人點游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自學咗1年50自28秒"},{"pid":"a59ebe3456bfc246da44486bc29ae9d6a4f1202e","tid":732112,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"用毛巾將臉部覆蓋，然後拿水澆灌在人臉上。水不斷湧入犯人體內，但是毛巾隔開了水，人吐不出來，呼吸也呼吸不了，僅有的空氣也被吸走，這種瀕臨死的感覺讓人崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n水刑能造成受刑人嘔吐咳嗽，甚至會從肺部及氣管分泌出鼻涕，更甚至能造成大小便失禁等生理反應。<br />\n<br />\n另外一種最 簡單的形勢就是施刑人一把抓住犯人的腦袋，將其整個往水裏塞，任憑其掙扎都不放手，看犯人快要斷氣之時，將其拉出水面讓其寬口氣，然後再次將其按入水中，這種被活活淹死的感受一般人不能承受。<br />\n<br />\n大量的水在人的胃中，肺中，氣管中肆意泛濫，水刺激着着這些氣管，讓人忍不住嘔吐和咳嗽，極難忍受。"},{"pid":"4cf80fa92689d1f16f80e21e2d7bc08a6cf1de32","tid":732112,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:23:13.000Z","msg":"一個星期學得識 唔怕死就識游<br />\n可以嘗試下係水入面開眼睇野"},{"pid":"7b212aecb5362426dd9db30e9f30c7ce2067f7c7","tid":732112,"uid":11578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"跳水池練膽，依家學埋潛水，之後想學埋free diving"},{"pid":"02c92a895940b2286c4d5efc9029ffe8b9e0c880","tid":732112,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"睇av學"},{"pid":"0780d7c7f42d47433935ce1b18b4e180b35a8239","tid":732112,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"男朋友教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e05a9453f98f88a485f179a9f3adc11b26d76b2","tid":732112,"uid":60674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d4a0e4e0aed9feec97bd9629aad6a5d89b91c36","tid":732112,"uid":138040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"我係上youtube 睇人點游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自學咗1年50自28秒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"自學一年50自28<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟操世界紀錄都比你破埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f26f4bf634b85be5c502fe24336d6eff72b664","tid":732112,"uid":167067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"四歲已經識游<br />\n7歲泳隊"},{"pid":"d75761b2525cef9b4f2f62dccab47611e6a1973c","tid":732112,"uid":138040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e05a9453f98f88a485f179a9f3adc11b26d76b2","tid":732112,"uid":60674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d4a0e4e0aed9feec97bd9629aad6a5d89b91c36","tid":732112,"uid":138040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"我係上youtube 睇人點游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自學咗1年50自28秒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"自學一年50自28<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟操世界紀錄都比你破埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"最盡28，依加點游都快唔到好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e64cf32b0a61b2a9df2229899bd574a54901e12","tid":732112,"uid":92278,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"學游水唔難 克服恐懼先最難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前都好驚水 但依家都識基本兩式<br />\n<br />\n我既方法就係:<br />\n<br />\n先練閉氣 靜坐時起碼頂到分半至兩分<br />\n<br />\n再去企到既池既池邊練潛水<br />\n成個人潛落去 開頭會緊張慢慢會習慣<br />\n順便數下自己潛左幾耐同時可令自己冷靜 <br />\n最重要可以埋女 <br />\n<br />\n潛到咁上下 可以頂到分半鐘到<br />\n就可以試下一啖氣式既游水<br />\n即係冇氣就企起身透氣 <br />\n算係可以係練下泳姿同冇咁悶<br />\n<br />\n一段時間後(我就一個暑假)<br />\n就應該冇咁驚水<br />\n因為你已大概掌握到<br />\n自己可以係水入面做到幾多野<br />\n<br />\n之後就可以睇youtube啲教學片自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我隔日游 一個月學識自由同蛙"},{"pid":"c2c0adc0cb2579bd509d0c73495018f0fb5aef29","tid":732112,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"18歲先識游水<br />\n<br />\n潛落水底睇人點游<br />\n<br />\n一直恐懼<br />\n<br />\n但數完手指關於時間方面就發覺冇得輸，之後學識左"},{"pid":"9023e150a6eedb305978ff517f195a13f67e6396","tid":732112,"uid":48817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"上游水堂學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}